Q4. Fix the below to alert Guvi geek
----------------------------------------------------------
fix.html
----------------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
 <script src=”script.js”></script>
</body>
</html>
----------------------------------------------------------
script.js
----------------------------------------------------------
let admin=9, fname=10.5; 
fname = "Guvi";
lname = "geek"
admin = fname+lname;
alert( admin ); // "Guvi geek"
----------------------------------------------------------
My Code:

let admin=9, fname=10.5; 
fname = "Guvi";
lname = "geek"
admin = fname+ " " + lname;
alert( admin );

