Q6. Fix the below to alert sum of two numbers
----------------------------------------------------------
fix.html
----------------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
 <script src=”script.js”></script>
</body>
</html>
----------------------------------------------------------
script.js
----------------------------------------------------------
let a = prompt("First number?");
let b = prompt("Second number?");
alert(a + b);
----------------------------------------------------------
My Code:

let a = parseInt(prompt("First number?"));
let b = parseInt(prompt("Second number?"));
alert(a + b);
